# CODEOWNERS for Kimika.
#
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners.
# Code owners are automatically requested for review whenever a pull
# request modifies the matched files, and combined with the
# "Require review from Code Owners" branch protection rule on `main`
# their approval becomes a hard requirement for merging.
#
# This catch-all rule keeps every file in the repository under the
# project owner's review until more granular ownership is needed.

